TITLE: Unrolling Loops in eBPF with Pragma Directive
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the #pragma unroll directive to unroll loops at compile time in eBPF programs. This technique was the main workaround before Linux v5.3 when bounded loops were not supported.
SOURCE: https://github.com/isovalent/ebpf-docs/blob/master/docs/linux/concepts/loops.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: c
