DESCRIPTION: Main packet processing logic that handles both IPv4 and IPv6 traffic, performs protocol parsing (TCP/UDP/ICMP), VIP lookup, and packet redirection. Includes tunnel key setting and statistics collection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/isovalent/ebpf-docs/blob/master/docs/linux/kfuncs/bpf_dynptr_from_skb.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: c
CODE:
