TITLE: Using bpf_probe_write_user in eBPF Program for Syscall Interception
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates the use of bpf_probe_write_user in an eBPF program attached to the exit of the open syscall. It intercepts the syscall for a specific process and overwrites the filename parameter with a new value.
SOURCE: https://github.com/isovalent/ebpf-docs/blob/master/docs/linux/helper-function/bpf_probe_write_user.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: c
