TITLE: Using bpf_probe_read_kernel in an XDP eBPF Program
DESCRIPTION: This eBPF program demonstrates the usage of 'bpf_probe_read_kernel' to access global kernel variables and variables from a loadable kernel module. It reads 'jiffies' and 'test_kmod_var' and prints their values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/isovalent/ebpf-docs/blob/master/docs/linux/helper-function/bpf_probe_read_kernel.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

