DESCRIPTION: Documents the BPF_F_STRICT_ALIGNMENT flag (introduced in v4.12) which enforces strict alignment checking during verification as if CONFIG_EFFICIENT_UNALIGNED_ACCESS is not set and NET_IP_ALIGN is defined as 2.
